# Line endings are LF everywhere — in the repository and in the working
# tree — so a checkout is byte-identical on Windows and Linux and nobody
# sees a file turn up modified with no real change.
#
# This overrides a contributor's core.autocrlf, which is why it belongs
# here rather than in each person's git config.

# ---- Text ----
* text=auto eol=lf

# ---- Binary ----
*.ico binary
